                             int holdability,
                             boolean autoCommit,
                             int transactionLevel)
                      throws java.sql.SQLException
        Creates a new prepared statement
        Parameters:
        sparql -
        connection - Connection
        type - Result Set type for result sets produced by this statement
        fetchDir - Fetch Direction
        fetchSize - Fetch Size
        holdability - Result Set holdability
        autoCommit - Auto-commit
        transactionLevel - Transaction Isolation level
        Throws:
        java.sql.SQLException - Thrown if there is a problem preparing the statement
